  Add ~ia64 keyword, requested by exg.

  13 Oct 2006; Emanuele Giaquinta <exg@gentoo.org> xdvik-22.84.10.ebuild:
  Drop lesstif USE flag and depend on virtual/motif.

  13 Oct 2006; Emanuele Giaquinta <exg@gentoo.org> xdvik-22.84.10.ebuild:
  Remove unneeded hack for lesstif.

  13 Oct 2006; Emanuele Giaquinta <exg@gentoo.org> xdvik-22.84.10.ebuild:
  Add a blocker on tetex built with X.

  09 Oct 2006; Emanuele Giaquinta <exg@gentoo.org> xdvik-22.84.10.ebuild:
  Correct X11 deps.

  07 Oct 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> xdvik-22.84.10.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd keyword.

